Hydrocortisone was granted FDA approval on 5 August 1952.[L10574]', '["S01CB03", "A01AC03", "S01BA02", "S01CA03", "D07AA02", "S01BB01", "D07XA01", "D07BA04", "S02CA03", "A07EA02", "S02BA01", "R01AD60", "H02AB09", "D07CA01", "S03CA04", "C05AA01"]', '[]');
